videos.description: Cincinnati's Gary Clark gets the steal on defense and finds Justin Jenifer in transition for the jump shot.
videos.headline: Clark's steal leads to Jenifer jumper

videos.description: After Jacob Evans misses his shot attempt, Kyle Washington grabs the offensive rebound and puts back up the layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Washington converts second-chance layup

videos.description: Cincinnati's Gary Clark gets the steal on the defensive end and sets up Jacob Evans in transition for the dunk.
videos.headline: Clark's hustle leads to Evans slam

videos.description: Alabama State's Fausto Pichardo grabs the offensive rebound and throws down the two-handed slam in the first half.
videos.headline: Pichardo throws down putback dunk

videos.description: Cincinnati's Gary Clark gets open off the pick and roll and spins right by Marice Wright for the layup.
videos.headline: Clark spins right by Wright for layup

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland sets up Jacob Evans behind the arc for a 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Cumberland sets up Evans for open three

videos.description: Trevor Moore and Jacob Evans force the turnover on the defensive end and Cane Broome finds Evans wide open in transition for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's defensive prowl leading to easy offense

videos.description: Ed Jones tries going up strong with the layup but is rejected by Cincinnati's Gary Clark in the second half.
videos.headline: Clark denies Jones at the rim

videos.description: Terrance LeFlore tries pulling up in transition but is denied by Cincinnati's Jacob Evans.
videos.headline: Evans stuffs LeFlore

videos.description: Cincinnati's Gary Clark blocks Gene Davis' shot attempt into the stands in the second half.
videos.headline: Clark rejects Davis with emphatic block

videos.description: Cincinnati's Cane Broome finds Keith Williams in transition for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Williams finishes crafty layup for and-1

videos.description: Keith Williams finds Justin Jenifer open behind the arch for a 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Jenifer extends Bearcats lead with 3-ball
